## The founder story

Acosa was born out of years on the road, arriving at accommodation that looked nothing like the photos, WiFi that collapsed during load shedding, and nowhere to work except the bed.

## The problem

Generic booking platforms are built for leisure. Their reviews tell you about the pool, not whether the generator covers the router.

## Our difference

We visit properties. We test the WiFi. We check the backup power actually switches over. Only then does a property earn its place on Acosa.

## Acosa Approved™

Our vetting framework scores every property against the practical standards that make or break a working trip.

## Business Traveller Essentials™

Reliable WiFi. Backup power. Secure parking. Workspace-friendly rooms. The essentials aren't nice-to-haves, they're the baseline.
